ults','<ul>\r\n	<li>Previne e soluciona deficiências antes de afetar o usuário final.</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensiona os recursos para o bom funcionamento da aplicação em produção.</li>\r\n	<li>Antevê o impacto do crescimento no comportamento da aplicação.</li>\r\n	<li>Auxilia a tomada de decisão de implantação de projetos (GO/NO GO) em comitês de GMUD.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1271,278,'_results','field_532f536cd9507'),(1272,278,'term','2 a 6 semanas. Pode ser realizado também em ambiente produtivo com variação de período.<b></b>'),(1273,278,'_term','field_532f537cd9508'),(1274,279,'_edit_last','2'),(1275,279,'_edit_lock','1397780453:2'),(1276,279,'efficiency','115'),(1277,279,'_efficiency','field_532f3f3cbd902'),(1278,279,'projects','a:11:{i:0;s:2:\"99\";i:1;s:3:\"126\";i:2;s:3:\"162\";i:3;s:3:\"159\";i:4;s:3:\"156\";i:5;s:3:\"153\";i:6;s:3:\"150\";i:7;s:3:\"147\";i:8;s:3:\"144\";i:9;s:3:\"141\";i:10;s:3:\"135\";}'),(1279,279,'_projects','field_532f43e46ccca'),(1280,279,'what_is_it','Identification and resolution of application bottlenecks. It is done with the application of synthetic loads in the environment and monitoring of all the infrastructure components (web server, application server, database, operating system, storage and network). Submits a report indicating volume of competing users supported by the environment, volume and response times of requisitions and transactions executed (throughput).'),(1281,279,'_what_is_it','field_532f337a3e604'),(1282,279,'what_is_it_for','<ul>\r\n	<li>Test behavior of applications with a high volume of users or data</li>\r\n	<li>Map the performance of the application in a new environment.</li>\r\n	<li>Identify bottlenecks in applications.</li>\r\n	<li>Measure the application’s capacity before it goes into production and correctly estimate the resources necessary for its use.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(1283,279,'_what_is_it_for','field_532f534fd9506'),(1284,279,'results','<ul>\r\n	<li>Prevents and resolves deficiencies before affecting the end user.